    <title>Centos7.2 hexo + Github 搭建个人博客</title>
    <link href="https://xiaoshen344.github.io/2018/07/19/hexo_git_blog/"/>
    <id>https://xiaoshen344.github.io/2018/07/19/hexo_git_blog/</id>
    <published>2018-07-18T16:56:53.140Z</published>
    <updated>2018-07-18T16:56:53.139Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-准备工作"><a href="#1-准备工作" class="headerlink" title="1.准备工作"></a>1.准备工作</h2><h3 id="1-1安装gcc-g"><a href="#1-1安装gcc-g" class="headerlink" title="1.1安装gcc-g++"></a>1.1安装gcc-g++</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install gcc-c++</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-2安装nodejs"><a href="#1-2安装nodejs" class="headerlink" title="1.2安装nodejs"></a>1.2安装nodejs</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://nodejs.org/dist/v8.1.2/node-v8.1.2.tar.gz  </span><br><span class="line">tar -zxvf node-v8.1.2.tar.gz  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> node-v8.1.2  </span><br><span class="line">mkdir -p /opt/node  </span><br><span class="line">./configure --prefix=/opt/node/  </span><br><span class="line">make &amp;&amp; make install  </span><br><span class="line">ln -s   /opt/node/lib/node_modules/npm/bin/npm-cli.js /usr/bin/npm  </span><br><span class="line">ln -s /opt/node/bin/node /usr/bin/node</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-3配置GitHub"><a href="#1-3配置GitHub" class="headerlink" title="1.3配置GitHub"></a>1.3配置GitHub</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name <span class="string">"xiaoshen344"</span>  </span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email <span class="string">"xiaoshen344@126.com"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将ssh的公钥拷贝至GitHub<br>可使用命令验证是否配置成功<br><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><h3 id="1-4安装hexo"><a href="#1-4安装hexo" class="headerlink" title="1.4安装hexo"></a>1.4安装hexo</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g  </span><br><span class="line">ln -s /opt/node/lib/node_modules/hexo-cli/bin/hexo /usr/bin/hexo  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /opt/node/  </span><br><span class="line">hexo init blog  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog/  </span><br><span class="line">npm install  </span><br><span class="line">hexo server  <span class="comment"># 启动hexo</span></span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="1-5-config-yml中配置deploy"><a href="#1-5-config-yml中配置deploy" class="headerlink" title="1.5_config.yml中配置deploy"></a>1.5_config.yml中配置deploy</h3><p>deploy:<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;type: git<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;repo: <a href="mailto:git@github.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">git@github.com</a>:xiaoshen344/xiaoshen344.github.io.git<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;branch: master  </p><h3 id="1-6将博客部署至GitHub"><a href="#1-6将博客部署至GitHub" class="headerlink" title="1.6将博客部署至GitHub"></a>1.6将博客部署至GitHub</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean      <span class="comment">#清除缓存文件 (db.json) 和已生成的静态文件 (public)  在某些情况（尤其是更换主题后），如果发现您对站点的更改无论如何也不生效，您可能需要运行该命令。  </span></span><br><span class="line">hexo generate   <span class="comment">#生成静态文件   </span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g   </span><br><span class="line">hexo server     <span class="comment">#启动服务器。默认情况下，访问网址为 http://localhost:4000/  </span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s  </span><br><span class="line">hexo deploy     <span class="comment">#部署到 github   </span></span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
